pros:
Your thoughts and ideas are always welcome;
Do what you do best and get support from your team to improve in areas that you might need it;
Everyone is relevant, everyone is connected, there's no way your success is only yours, everything we achieve is as a group;
Balance and personal lives taken into consideration;
I had an unforgettable time at Global Citizen Year, I keep the team that I worked with close to my heart and can say I made friends for life during my time there. They believe in my potential and nurtured my personal and professional dreams. I would work or volunteer anytime for them. You actually have a chance to do something to build a better future.
